and directories is subject to the BSD two-clause licence below except
for files derived from the Sail x86 model which are subject to the
terms of a BSD three-clause licence and additionally the licence of
the original ACL2 x86 model, from which the Sail model is generated
(see `sail-x86/model/LICENSE`).

